{"id":"luhith","term":"Luhith","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Made of boards, a Moabitish place between Zoar and Horonaim (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Isaiah 15:5\">Isa. 15:5</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Jeremiah 48:5\">Jer. 48:5</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Isaiah 15:5","Jeremiah 48:5"]}